<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ubranaganfoehammer.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Branagan Foehammer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#5F9EA0>(11/26/01 1:47:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=755.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Midgard info</span><hr size=1> I have Midgard characters currently on TWO different servers.  I have some on Kay, and on Tristan (think that is correct name).   I would love if some people would come to one of those servers so I could play with some friends there.  I also really have no desire to play on Test, as I dont want to have THREE sets of Midgard characters that I dont have time to play, as well as the RvR issue with hardly any people on it. <br>
